<th>Prerequisite</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Configuration keys</td>
<td>Make sure that the <strong>Asset configuration</strong> key is available under the <strong>Data Dictionary</strong> &gt; <strong>Configuration Keys</strong> node.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
